<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Email Verification</title>
</head>

<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(38, 38, 38); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; width: auto; max-width: 600px; padding: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 16px;">Dear <%= name %>,</p>
    <p style="font-size: 14px;">You have requested a password reset for your account. To confirm your request, please match one of the items
        displayed below with the one shown on our website.</p>

    <table role="presentation" style="width: 100%; border-spacing: 10px; text-align: center;">
        <tr>
            <% items?.forEach(element => { %>
                <td style="padding: 5px;">
                    <a href="https://craftdle-backend-production.up.railway.app/users/userVerify?token=<%= token %>&id=<%= element?.id %>">
                        <img src="https://craftdle-backend-production.up.railway.app/assets/items/<%= element?.src %>" 
                             alt="<%= element?.name %>" 
                             style="width: 100px; height: 100px; object-fit: contain; background-color: rgb(19, 19, 19); border: rgb(81, 81, 81) solid 3px; display: block; margin: 0 auto;">
                    </a>
                </td>
            <% }); %>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <div style="color: rgb(255, 85, 85); text-shadow: 0 0 5px #000000;">
        <p style="font-size: 14px;">If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email. Your account remains secure, and no
            changes will be made.</p>
        <p style="font-size: 14px;">If you believe this email was sent in error or you notice unusual activity on your account, please
            contact our support team immediately.</p>
    </div>

    <footer style="text-align: center; font-size: 12px;">
        <p>Thank you for using Craftdle!</p>
        <p>&copy; 2025 Craftdle. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>

</html>